column2: "I'm... dying... (wheeze) ...that spartan maniac is out of control!"
"Pay her no heed, <%me>. This is one of her duties as administrator."
"Field testing and training was part of the job description - were you not debriefed?"
"I admit it was mentioned, but nothing this extreme!"
"Your low stats are to blame. Notice how I am hardly breaking a sweat."
"Why thank you for not comparing a frail lady such as myself to a top-level athlete like you!!"
"Did you not choose this path? If you wish to quit, I will not stop you."
"Fine, fine!! I'll do it, alright? Satisfied?"
"<%me> dearest? Just you wait, I'll give it my all!"
"...Not a single word without a complaint. If I were to tolerate such behavior, it would only embolden her."
